	(text "Arguments for pin assignments:\n1. GPIO0 & GPIO1 cannot have int. pull-ups\n2. GPIO2 must be high at boot (ext. pulled up)\n3. GPIO8 must be high at boot (ext. pulled up)\n4. EN must be high at boot (ext. pulled up)\n5. GPIO9 must be high at boot (int. pulled up)\n6. we need 13 pin functions: \n     5x SPI\n     2x I2C (need ext. pullup)\n     3x display IO (busy act. H, rs act. L, D/C)\n     1x user button (2x1 analog multiplex)\n     1x boot button (GPIO9)\n     1x FLEX (frontlight, alarm, ...)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 184.404 65.786 0)
